<div id="toctitle">
<h2>תוכן עניינים</h2>
</div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="#.D7.9E.D7.99.D7.95.D7.97.D7.A1_.D7.9C.D7.A8.D7.A9.22.D7.99"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">מיוחס לרש"י</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="#.D7.A8.22.D7.9F"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">ר"ן</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#.D7.AA.D7.95.D7.A1.D7.A4.D7.95.D7.AA"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">תוספות</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#.D7.9E.D7.A7.D7.95.D7.A8.D7.95.D7.AA_.D7.95.D7.94.D7.A2.D7.A8.D7.95.D7.AA"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">מקורות והערות</span></a></li>
</ul>
</td>
